<HEAD2>(Performing Arithmetic Functions\performing_arith)

<p>
Perform arithmetic functions on Calculator just as 
you would on a handheld calculator:
<list>(numbered)
<le>Enter the first operand. It appears in the 
accumulator.
<le>Enter the function you want to perform. The functions are 
addition (+), subtraction (-), multiplication (*), and division (/).
<le>Enter the second operand. It appears in the 
accumulator.
<le>Enter the equal sign (=). The result appears in the 
accumulator.
<endlist>



