<head4>(Copy\copy)
<p>
To copy a number from 
Calculator's accumulator or memory to another application, choose Copy from 
the Edit menu as follows:
<list>(numbered)
<le>To highlight the number, click on either the accumulator or memory.
<le>To copy the highlighted
number, choose Copy.  You can then paste the number in another 
application's window.
<endlist>

