<head4>(Paste\paste)
<p>
To paste a number or an equation that
contains no variables from another application 
into Calculator's accumulator, choose Paste from the Edit menu.
<p>
To copy an equation or
number from another  application and to display the
result of the equation or the number in the accumulator: 

<list>(numbered)
<le>Select the equation or number to copy. 
<le>Choose Copy 
from the other applications's Edit menu to copy the highlighted 
information.
<le>Choose Paste from Calculator's Edit menu to enter
the result of the equation or the number to
the accumulator.
<endlist>

<P>
